pub -sub (publish subscribe). Develpoed by twitter.
Features: partioning,replication high throughput over point to point messaging system.
Usage: Tracking user activities on website.
       Aggregation of operational datasuch as call stacks erors cpu.
       Travel companies,banking  industry
       Can be used as : Stream processing,storage system,Messaging system
       
Kafka COntroller : The broker which manages the leader/follower relationship for all partitions.


Role of zookeeper: Electing controller.
                   Manages kafka cluster.
                    Keeps track of topics ,its partitions and replicas.
